/extras/9adcb09cec6fed5afd2de6dd8b68e10a.poster.avif?t=1550760540\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/889400/extras/9adcb09cec6fed5afd2de6dd8b68e10a.webm?t=1550760540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/889400/extras/9adcb09cec6fed5afd2de6dd8b68e10a.mp4?t=1550760540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/889400/extras/d55696ef5704067eba53450b95d6b37f.poster.avif?t=1550760540\" width=288 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/889400/extras/d55696ef5704067eba53450b95d6b37f.webm?t=1550760540\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/889400/extras/d55696ef5704067eba53450b95d6b37f.mp4?t=1550760540\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Surface climbing and momentum based system that enables unique acrobatic traversal.<br></li><li> Character class swapping mid-battle. 6 character classes to choose from.<br></li><li> Competitive online multiplayer.<br></li><li> Extensive and challenging single player mode.<br></li><li> Flying fists that can grabs character classes out of the air, push enemies, and pick up the ball.<br></li><li> Inspired by action classics such as Soldat, Abuse, Altitude, Teeworlds, and Quake.<br></li><li> Original soundtrack by Brian Woods (@over.and.out_), guitarist for the band You May Die in the Desert.</li></ul>",
